    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基本说明</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Standing Together</strong> 是一款自上而下的射击类合作 roguelite 游戏，在游戏中，您必须击败不断壮大的僵尸大军，防止一个地区被攻陷。游戏中获得的装备和消耗品会永久保存在您的背包中，并可带到下一局游戏中。您可以玩单人游戏，也可以玩最多四人的多人游戏。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与永久保存的背包不同，技能树的位置和获得的天赋在每次游戏时都会发生变化，因此每次都可以采取新的策略。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178670/extras/f426af915fdae16b0cb99cc1066bb75e.poster.avif?t=1760405935\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178670/extras/f426af915fdae16b0cb99cc1066bb75e.webm?t=1760405935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178670/extras/f426af915fdae16b0cb99cc1066bb75e.mp4?t=1760405935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178670/extras/ea104c2244c42cb5e78053095166ff7f.poster.avif?t=1760405935\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178670/extras/ea104c2244c42cb5e78053095166ff7f.webm?t=1760405935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178670/extras/ea104c2244c42cb5e78053095166ff7f.mp4?t=1760405935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会被派往一个区域，为了将僵尸数量控制在一定数量以下，你必须战斗数天。 白天，僵尸数量不会增加，也不会攻击你，但到了晚上，该区域的所有僵尸都会来杀你。在最后一天结束时，您就可以逃脱了。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >整个区域散落着各种补给和材料。白天，当僵尸安静下来时，您可以去种植物品。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178670/extras/5944610d97f7c25474324660f86f5737.poster.avif?t=1760405935\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178670/extras/5944610d97f7c25474324660f86f5737.webm?t=1760405935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178670/extras/5944610d97f7c25474324660f86f5737.mp4?t=1760405935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在该区域被占领之前杀死僵尸。您可以使用各种武器和物资清理僵尸，包括近战武器、手枪、步枪、霰弹枪和手榴弹。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在夜间，您偶尔会遇到麻烦的僵尸。但它们最终会被证明在烧焦的洗礼面前无能为力。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178670/extras/c8d3f1ac29ea77c3e2028720bf74795a.poster.avif?t=1760405935\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178670/extras/c8d3f1ac29ea77c3e2028720bf74795a.webm?t=1760405935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178670/extras/c8d3f1ac29ea77c3e2028720bf74795a.mp4?t=1760405935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着时间的推移，僵尸会变得越来越强大。但你可以比它们更强大。当你杀死僵尸时，你会获得经验，并解锁技能和共享特权。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你和你的队友可以完全共享福利。请明智选择。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178670/extras/d012b8f638dfd8f7cba0885aafa30854.poster.avif?t=1760405935\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178670/extras/d012b8f638dfd8f7cba0885aafa30854.webm?t=1760405935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178670/extras/d012b8f638dfd8f7cba0885aafa30854.mp4?t=1760405935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有时，设置路障和路障而不是四处游荡是个好主意。如果你的路障被摧毁了，别担心，你还有出路。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造路障所需的材料可以在整个区域或通过杀死僵尸找到。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178670/extras/d8cefd4b606703e6ac5504055d336002.poster.avif?t=1760405935\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178670/extras/d8cefd4b606703e6ac5504055d336002.webm?t=1760405935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178670/extras/d8cefd4b606703e6ac5504055d336002.mp4?t=1760405935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中获得的物品会储存在背包中并永久保存。 之前收集的物品可以在下一次派遣中使用。不过，前提是你必须在该区域存活下来。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武器在使用过程中会损耗耐久度，一旦损毁就无法使用。您应该准备几件武器。被毁坏的武器将在下一次派遣时修复。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >其他游戏信息</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当前版本中共有 6 种僵尸。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏开始前，您可以选择一个冰球卡组。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您在游戏过程中死亡或离开，您背包中的物品会保留您开始游戏前的状态。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在最后一天结束时，您将可以逃离该区域。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武器的耐久度会在下一次派遣时修复。 （仅限演示版）</p></li></ul>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 韩语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 日语, 简体中文, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 波兰语",
